==药理==
二甲双胍的分子药理机制目前尚不完全清楚。已知其至少作用于[[肝脏|肝脏]]，减少[[糖异生|糖异生]]（即葡萄糖的生产）与减轻[[胰岛素|胰岛素]]抵抗<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.onlineclinic.co.uk/metformin.html | publisher = OnlineClinic | title = How does this medication work? | accessdate = 2015-01-30 | archive-date = 2016-07-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160722062937/http://www.onlineclinic.co.uk/metformin.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。有研究表明二甲双胍可激活{{tsl|en|AMP-activated protein kinase|单磷酸腺苷活化的蛋白激酶}}（AMP-activated protein kinase，AMPK），是二甲双胍抑制肝脏糖异生、在胰岛素信号传导通路中提高胰岛素的敏感性不可缺少的机制之一<ref name="Zhou">{{cite journal | vauthors = Zhou G, Myers R, Li Y, Chen Y, Shen X, Fenyk-Melody J, Wu M, Ventre J, Doebber T, Fujii N, Musi N, Hirshman MF, Goodyear LJ, Moller DE | display-authors = 6 | title = Role of AMP-activated protein kinase in mechanism of metformin action | journal = The Journal of Clinical Investigation | volume = 108 | issue = 8 | pages = 1167–74 | date = October 2001 |language=en | pmid = 11602624 | pmc = 209533 | doi = 10.1172/JCI13505 }}</ref>。AMPK作为[[蛋白激酶|蛋白激酶]]不仅在胰岛素信号传导通路中，在全身能量平衡以及葡萄糖和脂肪的代谢中也起着重要作用<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Towler MC, Hardie DG | title = AMP-activated protein kinase in metabolic control and insulin signaling | journal = Circulation Research | volume = 100 | issue = 3 | pages = 328–41 | date = February 2007 |language=en | pmid = 17307971 | doi = 10.1161/01.RES.0000256090.42690.05 }}</ref>。动物实验和临床研究均表明二甲双胍可诱导糖尿病的粪便微生物菌群构成发生重大变化，不仅可能有助于[[胰高血糖素样肽-1|胰高血糖素样肽-1]]（GLP-1）的分泌及作用，还证实可改善胰岛素的敏感性，也是其抗2型糖尿病作用的重要机制之一<ref name ="Burcelin">{{cite journal | vauthors = Burcelin R | title = The antidiabetic gutsy role of metformin uncovered? | journal = Gut | volume = 63 | issue = 5 | pages = 706–7 | date = May 2014 |language=en | pmid = 23840042 | doi = 10.1136/gutjnl-2013-305370 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |title=Metformin alters the gut microbiome of individuals with treatment-naive type 2 diabetes, contributing to the therapeutic effects of the drug |url=https://www.nature.com/articles/nm.4345 |last=Wu |first=Hao |last2=Esteve |first2=Eduardo |date=2017-07 |journal=Nature Medicine |issue=7 |doi=10.1038/nm.4345 |volume=23 |pages=850–858 |language=en |issn=1546-170X |last3=Tremaroli |first3=Valentina |last4=Khan |first4=Muhammad Tanweer |last5=Caesar |first5=Robert |last6=Mannerås-Holm |first6=Louise |last7=等 |access-date=2021-04-11 |archive-date=2017-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171211103001/https://www.nature.com/articles/nm.4345 }}</ref>。

==优势==
* 不会增加体重
* 与其他药品相比不易造成低血糖
* 减少三酸甘油酯
* 对低密度脂蛋白有很好的效果
* 对血压无影响
* 价格低廉

==缺点==
* 患中到重度肾脏疾病或心脏病者忌用，因为可能由于[[酗酒|酗酒]]导致[[乳酸|乳酸]]性[[酸中毒|酸中毒]]。
* 肠胃道症狀，包括噁心、腹泻、腹痛
* [[维生素B12|维生素B12]]缺乏
* 金属味觉

==抗衰老研究==
一些資料顯示，服用二甲双胍的糖尿病患者，其[[存活率|存活率]]甚至超過其他条件类似但未患糖尿病的人群<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Can people with type 2 diabetes live longer than those without? A comparison of mortality in people initiated with metformin or sulphonylurea monotherapy and matched, non-diabetic controls|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25041462/|last=Bannister|first=C. A.|last2=Holden|first2=S. E.|date=2014-11|journal=Diabetes, Obesity & Metabolism|issue=11|doi=10.1111/dom.12354|volume=16|pages=1165–1173|issn=1463-1326|pmid=25041462|last3=Jenkins-Jones|first3=S.|last4=Morgan|first4=C. Ll|last5=Halcox|first5=J. P.|last6=Schernthaner|first6=G.|last7=Mukherjee|first7=J.|last8=Currie|first8=C. J.|access-date=2021-08-12|archive-date=2022-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220405005708/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25041462/}}</ref>，而對二甲双胍在人類身上是否有抗[[衰老|衰老]]效果的臨床實驗預計於2016年冬在美國開始進行。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2015/12-02/7652205.shtml |title=世界首例抗衰老药将临床试验 或让人活到120岁 |publisher=中新網 |date=2015-12-02 |accessdate=2015-12-02 |archive-date=2020-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916131723/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2015/12-02/7652205.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

